<p>Statistics is widely used in many fields:</p>

<ul>
<li>Business analytics</li>
<li>Medical research</li>
<li>Economics</li>
<li>Machine learning</li>
<li>Government planning</li>
</ul>

<h2>8.6 Summary</h2>

<p>
In this chapter we studied key statistical concepts and tools
used to analyze data effectively. These tools help transform
raw numerical information into meaningful insights.
</p>

<p>
Mastering these ideas is essential for further statistical analysis.
</p>

